<!-- §8 Why people are buying — problem this solves -->
<h2>Why Are Sleep Masks Boring When They Don't Have to Be?</h2>
<p>Sleep gear is usually clinical and colorless. A standard black sleep mask doesn't spark joy — it just sits in your drawer looking utilitarian. At the same time, kids and teens resist wearing "adult" sleep accessories unless they feel personal, fun, or gift-worthy. The Animal Headband Sleep Mask solves this by combining personality with legitimate function.</p>
