<!-- §9 What is [Product]? -->
<h2>What Is the Animal Headband Sleep Mask?</h2>
<p>The Animal Headband Sleep Mask is a plush Bluetooth sleep mask with five animal-themed designs. It's built for comfort and fun: flat 24ohm/30mm speakers for clear audio, Bluetooth 5.0 for stable connectivity up to 20 meters, and a soft plush headband that stays in place. The mask provides full blackout coverage and charges in 1.5 hours for up to 6 hours of playback time. It's positioned as a statement piece — part gift item, part functional sleep tool.</p>

